properties.template:
{% set n = cur_keyframes|length %}
{% set cols = ceil(sqrt(n))|int %}
{% set rows = ceil(n / cols)|int %}
{% set orientation = "HORIZONTAL (landscape, 16:9)" %}
Generate a single {{ orientation }} image containing a {{ cols }}x{{ rows }} grid of animation keyframes for a music video.

IMAGE ORIENTATION: {{ orientation }}.

CHARACTER BIBLE:
{% for char in character_bible %}
{{ char.name }}: {{ char.description }}
{% endfor %}

STYLE GUIDE:
{{ style_guide }}

GRID LAYOUT:
{{ cols }} columns x {{ rows }} rows. Panels must be flush edge-to-edge with NO gaps, borders, margins, or spacing between them.
Each panel occupies exactly 1/{{ cols }} of the width and 1/{{ rows }} of the height.
Each panel is a {{ orientation }} frame.
All panels must share the same art style, color palette, and character designs for visual consistency.

PANELS:
{% for kf in cur_keyframes %}
    {% set r = loop.index0 // cols + 1 %}
    {% set c = loop.index0 % cols + 1 %}
Panel ({{ r }},{{ c }}) — Keyframe {{ kf.idx }}: {{ kf.image_prompt }}
{% endfor %}

IMPORTANT:
Generate exactly one {{ orientation }} image with all {{ n }} panels arranged in a {{ cols }}x{{ rows }} grid with NO borders or gaps.
Maintain consistent character appearances and art style across all panels.
